data.description: Come take a look a this spacious all brick raised ranch in desirable Clearing area. The first floor features a spacious living room, 3 bedrooms, and 1 full bath. The open and bright kitchen with an eating area are perfect place for meals and gatherings. The kitchen features white cabinets, a nice backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The fully finished basement offers extra living space with 2 bedrooms, a 1 full bath, and a family room perfect for entertaining. The fenced-in yard with a concrete patio and pool make the perfect summer area. This home offers plenty of storage, some updates, a 2 car garage and more!. The windows and doors were installed by the airport to reduce noise. This home is walking distance to schools, shopping and dining.
